[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/rest">Rest</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/rest">Rest</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user goes to sleep for two turns. It fully restores the user's HP and heals any status problem.</p>